            "creation_date": 1386315565,
            "body": "<p>Given this definition<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>public &lt;T extends MyObject&gt; T  getResult(Class&lt;T&gt; class, String id)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>You need to pass the class of an Object of type (or a sub-type of) MyObject and String. Something like <code>getResult(MyObject.class, \"pickles\");<\/code>. The method then must return an instance of MyObject (or a sub-class).<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 20418599,
            "question_id": 20418544
        },
