            "creation_date": 1386315570,
            "body": "<p>You can invoke your method like below<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>MyObject result = getResult(MyObject.class, \"myId\");\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Here is a shot explaination of your method <code>getResult<\/code><\/p>\n\n<ul>\n<li><em>Param 1<\/em> - takes any class of type <code>MyObject<\/code>  <\/li>\n<li><em>Param 2<\/em> - takes any String<\/li>\n<li><em>Retruns<\/em> - an Object of type <code>MyObject<\/code>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
